-- Finmeccanica May Get $122 Million in Panama Defense Orders, Sole Reports
-- Sonia Sirletti
-- 2010-07-01T06:01:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/finmeccanica-may-get-122-million-in-panama-defense-orders-sole-reports.html

          
          
             Finmeccanica SpA may get contracts in
Panama worth more than 100 million euros ($122 million), Il Sole
24 Ore reported, without saying where it got the information.  
 The orders, related to national defense, will follow a
cooperation agreement signed yesterday between the two
countries, the daily reported.  
          
          


  


        